               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction (fols. 2ra-10va)
 - Mäqdǝmä Wängel “Introduction to
                     the Gospel” (fols. 2ra-6rb)
 - Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols.
                     6rb-6vb)
 - The “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 6vb-7ra)
 - On the
                     Reliability of the Gospels (fols. 7ra-7va)
 - Canon tables (fols.
                     8ra-10va)
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 10vb-59va)
 - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 69 titles (fols. 10vb-11rb)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 12ra-59rb)
 - Short postscript (fols.
                     59rb-59va)
 III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 59va-85ra)
 - Biography of Mark
                     (fols. 59va-59vb)
 - Biography of Luke (fols. 60ra-60va)
 - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 84 titles (fols. 60va-61rb)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 62ra-85ra)
 - Short postscript (fol.
                     85ra)
 IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 86ra-113vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās “Gospel
                     of Luke” (fols. 86ra-113vb)
 - Short postscript (fol. 113vb)
 V) Gospel
                     of John (fols. 115ra-137ra)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols.
                     122ra-152va)
 - Short postscript (fol. 137ra)
 
 Additiones
                     1-5.</summary>
